1
00:00:10,360 --> 00:00:11,040
Li Jing

2
00:00:12,160 --> 00:00:12,960
Yu Han

3
00:00:13,600 --> 00:00:14,560
My time

4
00:00:15,160 --> 00:00:15,720
is running out

5
00:00:16,920 --> 00:00:17,800
Yu Han

6
00:00:17,800 --> 00:00:18,840
You won't die

7
00:00:18,840 --> 00:00:20,160
You will get better

8
00:00:23,760 --> 00:00:24,560
Li Jing

9
00:00:25,160 --> 00:00:26,440
Do you remember

10
00:00:27,120 --> 00:00:28,960
our engagement?

11
00:00:29,440 --> 00:00:30,360
I remember

12
00:00:31,840 --> 00:00:32,520
Then

13
00:00:32,960 --> 00:00:34,160
when will you

14
00:00:34,160 --> 00:00:35,960
marry me?

15
00:00:36,720 --> 00:00:37,840
Right now

16
00:00:37,840 --> 00:00:39,280
Right here

17
00:00:39,280 --> 00:00:40,240
we get married

18
00:00:43,400 --> 00:00:44,200
Yu Han

19
00:00:44,200 --> 00:00:44,920
Look

20
00:00:58,360 --> 00:00:59,360
Heavenly fire tempers the essence

21
00:00:59,360 --> 00:01:00,440
Softening to circle the finger

22
00:01:00,440 --> 00:01:01,040
Rise

23
00:01:01,440 --> 00:01:02,600
To hold your hand

24
00:01:03,440 --> 00:01:04,680
and grow old with you

25
00:01:07,560 --> 00:01:09,000
Husband

26
00:01:09,400 --> 00:01:10,400
Wife

27
00:01:40,640 --> 00:01:41,440
Er Tiao

28
00:02:02,040 --> 00:02:03,480
Do not harm my son

29
00:02:12,120 --> 00:02:12,960
It's the Dragon King

30
00:02:12,960 --> 00:02:14,040
The Dragon King is here

31
00:02:16,360 --> 00:02:17,360
The Dragon King is here

32
00:02:21,240 --> 00:02:22,240
Ao Guang

33
00:02:22,240 --> 00:02:23,680
You dare set foot in the Divine Land?

34
00:02:24,000 --> 00:02:26,000
Do you not fear suppression by Celestial Laws?

35
00:02:26,400 --> 00:02:28,000
A mere Mystical Bird

36
00:02:28,680 --> 00:02:30,200
dares to make such noise?

37
00:02:36,400 --> 00:02:38,920
The Human Race disrespects gods and spirits

38
00:02:38,920 --> 00:02:40,280
and deserves death

39
00:02:49,880 --> 00:02:50,960
How is this possible?

40
00:02:51,560 --> 00:02:52,320
Zhu Que

41
00:02:52,920 --> 00:02:54,040
is still alive?

42
00:03:04,640 --> 00:03:06,040
Ao Guang of the East Sea

43
00:03:06,040 --> 00:03:08,040
congratulates the Divine Lord

44
00:03:08,040 --> 00:03:09,960
on returning from Nirvana

45
00:03:12,240 --> 00:03:14,120
It actually returned from Nirvana

46
00:03:14,400 --> 00:03:16,000
Regarding today's matter

47
00:03:16,000 --> 00:03:16,760
I'm afraid...

48
00:03:17,040 --> 00:03:18,600
Your Majesty

49
00:03:18,600 --> 00:03:21,120
Since Divine Lord Zhu Que has appeared

50
00:03:21,120 --> 00:03:22,000
why not

51
00:03:22,000 --> 00:03:23,440
cease hostilities here?

52
00:03:24,480 --> 00:03:26,960
Your Majesty's divine might is fearless

53
00:03:26,960 --> 00:03:28,240
but our sons of the East Sea

54
00:03:28,240 --> 00:03:31,160
may not withstand the might of Zhu Que's divine fire

55
00:03:31,160 --> 00:03:32,920
Even if Your Majesty wins

56
00:03:32,920 --> 00:03:35,720
the East Sea will suffer great losses

57
00:03:35,720 --> 00:03:37,920
At that time, the Heavenly Court and Western Sects

58
00:03:37,920 --> 00:03:39,840
might seize the opportunity to invade

59
00:03:39,840 --> 00:03:42,360
Good for nothing but ruining things

60
00:03:43,160 --> 00:03:45,680
Xiao Jiu actually provoked such an ancient deity

61
00:03:56,400 --> 00:03:57,240
Xiao Jiu

62
00:03:57,760 --> 00:03:58,440
Come back

63
00:04:00,600 --> 00:04:02,160
Ao Guang of the East Sea

64
00:04:02,480 --> 00:04:04,920
invites the leader of the Human Race

65
00:04:04,920 --> 00:04:06,440
for a face-to-face talk

66
00:04:17,360 --> 00:04:21,560
Li Jing of Chentang Pass is here

67
00:04:21,960 --> 00:04:23,360
Li Jing

68
00:04:23,360 --> 00:04:26,360
The Human Race and Sea Clan have no old grudges

69
00:04:26,480 --> 00:04:29,080
This was merely a misunderstanding

70
00:04:29,560 --> 00:04:30,720
Are you willing

71
00:04:30,720 --> 00:04:33,040
to make peace here?

72
00:04:33,040 --> 00:04:34,840
Make peace?

73
00:04:34,840 --> 00:04:37,080
The Sea Clan raised troops to invade my Chentang Pass

74
00:04:37,200 --> 00:04:39,360
How many innocent commoners died tragically?

75
00:04:39,760 --> 00:04:42,400
My Human Race soldiers' casualties lie in heaps

76
00:04:42,840 --> 00:04:44,840
You lightly call it a misunderstanding

77
00:04:45,280 --> 00:04:46,840
Don't think you can brush this off

78
00:04:46,960 --> 00:04:48,840
My son Xiao Jiu

79
00:04:48,960 --> 00:04:50,560
is young and ignorant

80
00:04:50,880 --> 00:04:52,560
and did not intend this

81
00:04:53,200 --> 00:04:56,360
This King will surely discipline him strictly

82
00:04:56,360 --> 00:04:58,000
Do you think we don't know?

83
00:04:58,360 --> 00:04:59,480
You raised troops

84
00:04:59,480 --> 00:05:01,160
intending to drown the Nine Provinces

85
00:05:01,160 --> 00:05:02,880
and seize my Human Race's divine position

86
00:05:03,160 --> 00:05:05,400
My Dragon Clan is a born divine race

87
00:05:05,960 --> 00:05:07,800
The Four Seas have been at peace for too long

88
00:05:08,080 --> 00:05:09,560
the divine positions were set long ago

89
00:05:09,560 --> 00:05:11,400
This is the injustice of the Heavenly Way

90
00:05:11,760 --> 00:05:14,760
This King only wants to take back what is rightfully ours

91
00:05:14,760 --> 00:05:16,240
You are clearly bullying the weak

92
00:05:16,240 --> 00:05:17,440
acts of banditry

93
00:05:18,000 --> 00:05:20,200
This King asks you one last time

94
00:05:21,120 --> 00:05:22,720
Today, is it war

95
00:05:22,880 --> 00:05:24,240
or peace?
